<li id="cite_note-13"><b><a href="#cite_ref-13" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.earstudio.com/sanjosesemaphore/decoding.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.earstudio.com/sanjosesemaphore/decoding.pdf" rel="nofollow">(PDF) A paper, written by the two men who discovered it, describes the decoding of the code and reveals the answer</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-14"><b><a href="#cite_ref-14" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.earstudio.com/sanjosesemaphore/report.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.earstudio.com/sanjosesemaphore/report.pdf" rel="nofollow">(PDF) The two men to discover the encoded message</a></li>
</ol>
